name: Scarlett Plug-in Suite License File
summary: Learn about .FNLF files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: You can install your FLNF software license file by opening Scarlett Plug-in Suite and clicking the "Install License File" button. Once installed, the button goes away. If you don't have a software license the first time you open the software, a software activation box will appear and you can submit an activation request and then install the retrieved license file.
